="preserve">Al-Gharafa Sports Club is a professional sports club based in Doha, Qatar which plays in the Qatar Star League and is one of the most successful in the history of Qatar football, winning many trophies. Al-Gharafa has won a Sixteen titles, seven QSL League, Six Prince Cups, two Crown Pirnce Cups and one Arab league Cup.
Al-Gharafa S.C. is a football club which plays in Qatar.
